{"tid":929046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ Intel 大裁員？傳市場部門裁減 2/3 員工！","createTime":"2018-12-05T09:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T08:35:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"220f5051e85b36dfee63d50a7101b3341ca5d6b5","tid":929046,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"Dec 5, 2018<br />\nIntel 近年雖然仍然是 CPU 界的王者，不過 AMD 正在不斷追趕下，Intel 不得不提升開發速度應戰，不過近日卻有消息顯示，Intel 將會大裁員，將市場部門的原有90多人團隊將精簡至30人，將目標集中在企業級客戶中，減少消費級市場的資源。<br />\n<br />\nAdage網站的報導，表示 Intel 正在改革內部的市場部團隊Agency Inside，現有的90多人團隊將會大幅縮減到只保留30人，改革的目的是集中關注企業級市場，未來會更少資源投向消費級市場，相信是因為消費市場正在不斷縮小所導致。<br />\n<br />\n智能手機及平板電腦的出現下，一般用戶可以在手機上，完成大部份過去只能在電腦完成的工作，因此，消費市場對電腦的需求正在不斷減少，Intel 將資源集中在企業客戶，只可說時代及潮流改變的結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/05/intel-cut-man-power/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F12%2F05%2Fintel-cut-man-power%2F&d=9DBRqKeZ%2Fbmcg3Dx4ivvIk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c2fdd6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/12/05/intel-cut-man-power/</a>"},{"pid":"ecf27d52d3607ce965a1c6b4b6f2b3e1051c3fbc","tid":929046,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"World No IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7306962f9e0014b5000a2f3a5f96d423051a50fe","tid":929046,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"唔係炒"},{"pid":"f1d2e2dc4eb8b4c5ab317709073ef01e197f8658","tid":929046,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7306962f9e0014b5000a2f3a5f96d423051a50fe","tid":929046,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-